import { useState } from "react"; import { useNavigate, useLocation } from "react-router-dom"; function EditContact({ onSave }) { const navigate = useNavigate(); const initialContact = useLocation().state; const [contact, setContact] = useState(initialContact); const inputChange = (e) => { const { name, value } = e.target; setContact({ ...contact, [name]: value, }); }; const onSubmit = async (e) => { e.preventDefault(); try { navigate("/"); } catch (error) { console.error(error.message); } }; return (
); } export default EditContact;
